data.description: Gorgeous waterfront home in sought after Courthouse Estates! Drive down the charming tree lined streets and pull into the home you've been waiting for! This fantastic floor plan leaves each room feeling bright, airy and welcoming. The first floor boasts a formal living room, large dining room, spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops as well as a cozy den with fireplace! Upstairs you'll find spacious bedrooms including the primary with a large walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom that has been beautifully updated! Step outside to see all that this large fenced in yard has to offer.  You'll love the patio area with firepit surrounded by lush grass and the serene lake! Top rated Kellam High School district and many upgrades including: HVAC 2019, WH 2023, Fireplace/Mantle 2021, Windows 2020, Doors 2020, Flooring 2019, Roof 2017, Siding 2017 You will love this home!! Call today to see it in person!
